The paper discusses a new multiplexing methodology for optical fiber transmission systems, which is a topic closely related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). Finally, the paper discusses the transmission of signals over long distances, which is a topic related to optical networking and high-speed communication (cs.OH).
